{"tid":619342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比人偷野放左上網賣(報左警都幫我五到）","createTime":"2018-04-06T14:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T17:55:27.000Z","uid":157415,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"976a4e78d7ef2ae34a4d0372f685f914a0082b78","tid":619342,"uid":157415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"比人偷野即日放左上網賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好無助<br />\n話說小弟秘撈某外賣速遞公司，有個保溫箱，原本有2個密碼鎖頭鎖住左，前幾日5點幾落樓準備拎車開工發現個保溫箱比人爆開左偷左d野<br />\n因為趕住開工無去報警，<br />\n入面放左一個 電單車冚，偈油同某外賣速遞公司風褸制服都比人偷左<br />\n隔左唔夠2個鐘發現有人放左個3樣野上某app拍賣<br />\n其中一件仲係公司制服，唔係人人有，所以有同事發現到話咗比我知，最終諗咗20幾個鐘覺得唔對路要去報警，點知警察同我講你冇證據證明嗰啲係你，都冇乜機會幫到你拉佢，我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n件公司制服要300按金㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個保溫箱可能有單車所鎖住佢偷唔到走，但係嗰兩個鎖頭一定要有工具先爆得到人手冇可能冇可能爆得到<br />\n條友應該係慣犯黎，睇返佢拍賣啲野都係好似老鼠貨，我懷疑條友住係地圖個點附近<br />\n佢應該係一個成年嘅男人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">知情者勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/220031_a8f864691a6f3909f30a1b0ebcb40839.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F220031_a8f864691a6f3909f30a1b0ebcb40839.png&h=15d9c0fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/220032_bc02eed12fb631491f8805060fedb22e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F220032_bc02eed12fb631491f8805060fedb22e.png&h=eda2c7bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/220759_36ab520edfcbd714322850fa902e7e81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F220759_36ab520edfcbd714322850fa902e7e81.png&h=9804e38e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/220802_0d72c6d1865b891b09c79b500a6ff9e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F220802_0d72c6d1865b891b09c79b500a6ff9e5.png&h=8ae63736&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/220803_857a6331fba41cfa255669a07e468a7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F220803_857a6331fba41cfa255669a07e468a7b.png&h=fc127d74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/220804_388e672ba10a2b75a130017a9c28fb01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F220804_388e672ba10a2b75a130017a9c28fb01.png&h=cc430df5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/220805_10588618994a6082463bc2e0da1d05e4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F220805_10588618994a6082463bc2e0da1d05e4.png&h=6ff5dd4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4dabb758c82fa60eadfd744adfcbb7aa086a684","tid":619342,"uid":42318,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:22:48.000Z","msg":"五乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3d1a85666c5b4